item.title: Project 1
item.description: My first “real” project in terms of finding a dataset and turning it into something. This is something I’ve been saying I’ll do for a while and I finally forced myself to just start and see where it goes. Regardless of what the outcome was, I simply knew that starting 1 project would lead to working on more and improving as I went. My goal was to keep it simple.
